  - timeout
  - huge stdout/stderr (how we handle it)
- Where result files live and how to inspect them
- How capture relates to interpretation (separate step)

---

# Acceptance criteria
- [ ] Operators understand the safety model and failure modes
- [ ] Runbook contains copy/paste examples
